00:39:57.680 --> 00:39:59.240 line:20%
City bertanding melawan Brentford

00:39:59.320 --> 00:40:01.440 line:20%
di mana jika mereka menang,
mereka teratas.

00:40:01.520 --> 00:40:03.160
Setidaknya beberapa jam.

